<br>Chinese dictionary definition of words<br>sad<br>Kangxi dictionary interpretation of words<br>sad<br>Source glyph<br>sad<br>Name meaning<br>The appearance of Yunyu's rise. cold. Quiet and cold.</div>\n</div>\n<div></div>\n<hr>\n<div id=\"bkrs_pinyin\">qī</div>\n<div id=\"bkrs_transl\">\n  <div><strong>I</strong><i> прил./наречие</i></div>\n  <div>холодный, прохладный; холодно, прохладно</div>\n  <div><span class=\"example-item\">凄其以风 * холодно в нём (<i>платье из тонкой или редкой ткани</i>) на ветру</span></div>\n  <div><span class=\"example-item\">秋日凄且厉 осенние дни холодны и гнетущи</span></div>\n  <div><strong>II</strong><i> гл.</i></div>\n  <div>1) смущаться, собираться (<i>о тучах</i>); затягиваться тучами (<i>о небе</i>)</div>\n  <div><span class=\"example-item\">有渰凄凄 сгущаются тучи, всё темней и темней</span></div>\n  <div>2) убиваться, скорбеть, горевать, печалиться</div>\n  <div><span class=\"example-item\">不独凄凉眼前事 скорблю не только о том, что перед глазами</span></div>\n</div>\n<hr>\n<hr><span class=\"text\"><b>Radicals:</b></span>\n<font color=\"#0a9ce6\"><span class=\"hiragana\"><b>冫, 妻</b></span> <span class=\"radical_icons\"></span></font>&nbsp;<span class=\"text\">(ice, wife)</span><br><u><span class=\"tiny\"><b>Meaning Mnemonic</b></span></u><br><span class=\"tiny\">Your <span class=\"radical-highlight\" rel=\"tooltip\" title=\"Radical\">ice</span> <span class=\"radical-highlight\" rel=\"tooltip\" title=\"Radical\">wife</span> is <span class=\"kanji-highlight\" rel=\"tooltip\" title=\"Kanji\">amazing</span>. She's also <span class=\"kanji-highlight\" rel=\"tooltip\" title=\"Kanji\">terrible</span>, because she's very cold and has many ice powers, but that's also part of what makes her amazing!<br><i>Picture your amazing and terrible ice wife. She's floating in your backyard cackling and shooting ice all around.</i></span><br><u><span class=\"tiny\"><b>Reading Mnemonic</b></span></u><br><span class=\"tiny\">She turns her <span class=\"kanji-highlight\" rel=\"tooltip\" title=\"Kanji\">amazing</span> gaze onto your <span class=\"reading-highlight\" rel=\"tooltip\" title=\"Reading\">sa</span>ber (<span lang=\"ja\">せい</span>) and hits it with an ice beam. Woah! Instead of turning to ice or shattering, it steals her awful powers. Now your saber is amazing and terrible too!<br><i>Now you're floating in the backyard cackling with your amazing wife as you use your terrible saber and freeze things with her!</i></span><br>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.mdbg.net/chinese/dictionary?page=worddict&wdrst=0&wdqtm=0&wdqcham=1&wdqt=\">MDBG</a> | <a href=\"https://bkrs.info/slovo.php?ch=凄\">BKRS</a> | <a href=\"https://dictionary.writtenchinese.com/#sk=凄&svt=pinyin\">WriCh</a> | <a href=\"http://www.qianyix.com/words/index.php?q=凄\">Qianyix</a> | <a href=\"https://www.yellowbridge.com/chinese/sentsearch.php?word=凄\">YBridge</a> | <a href=\"http://cca.xingtanlu.cn/?action=page&pid=8&do=search&name=凄\">Collocs</a> | <a href=\"https://characterpop.com/explode/凄\">ChPop</a> | <a href=\"https://visualchinesesearch.com/?query=凄\">SimCh</a> | <a href=\"http://www.hanzicraft.com/character/凄\">Stats</a> | <a href=\"https://www.google.com.au/search?q=凄&tbm=isch\">Google Images</a> | <a href=\"https://namakajiri.net/kanjigen/#凄\">Char lookup site</a></p>\n<div class=\"notes optional small\">冫 (лёд), 十 (десять), 女 (женщина), ヨ</div>\n<div class=\"notes optional\">Реже: 淒 (さむい、すごい、セイ、サイ ужасный). Не путать: 妻 (つま、サイ жена, супруга), 棲 (すむ、セイ обитать).</div>","glyphs":[{"glyph":"冫","pinyins":["bing1"]},{"glyph":"妻","pinyins":["qi1","qi4"]}],"isMentionedAt__hanziyuan_without_charactersWithComponent":["悽","淒"]}